296
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:41,000
In truth,

297
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,270
you and I

298
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,680
are very much alike.

299
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:50,320
I

300
00:18:50,350 --> 00:18:52,810
am not worthy
to be compared to Your Majesty.

301
00:18:53,370 --> 00:18:55,770
I cannot change your decision.

302
00:18:56,170 --> 00:18:57,740
But this life

303
00:18:58,370 --> 00:18:59,740
is still mine to decide.

304
00:19:01,330 --> 00:19:02,690
General Mo.

305
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:06,390
Even if you had power
that reached the heavens,

306
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:08,390
you are still a woman.

307
00:19:08,710 --> 00:19:10,200
And women

308
00:19:10,220 --> 00:19:12,140
cannot escape marriage.

309
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:14,750
If you had a marriage contract,

310
00:19:15,170 --> 00:19:18,100
I might be able
to help refuse on your behalf.

311
00:19:18,530 --> 00:19:20,010
What a pity!

312
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:24,000
But don't forget, Empress Dowager.

313
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:25,410
To the people,

314
00:19:25,950 --> 00:19:27,410
I am a general first,

315
00:19:27,870 --> 00:19:29,380
and a woman second.

316
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,090
You said you had a way

317
00:19:35,530 --> 00:19:37,530
to stop Feng Shiye from marrying me?

318
00:19:38,630 --> 00:19:39,430
Yes.

319
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,540
What way?

320
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:47,450
I'll go to the Empress Dowager

321
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:48,510
and...

322
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,510
And offer her

323
00:19:50,870 --> 00:19:52,200
Prince Jing's title.

324
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,070
She might agree...

325
00:19:54,090 --> 00:19:54,680
Agree to...

326
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:56,070
Prince Jing's title?

327
00:19:56,970 --> 00:19:58,830
You're willing to give up so much?

328
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:00,640
In exchange for what?

329
00:20:01,910 --> 00:20:02,780
For...

330
00:20:08,170 --> 00:20:09,000
Say it.

331
00:20:09,490 --> 00:20:10,340
For what?

332
00:20:11,740 --> 00:20:12,780
For marrying...

333
00:20:16,310 --> 00:20:17,370
Looks like we won't

334
00:20:17,570 --> 00:20:19,050
be having perch today

335
00:20:37,790 --> 00:20:39,180
That Mo Qingchuan.

336
00:20:39,300 --> 00:20:40,830
What kind of heroine is she?

337
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:42,560
No integrity at all.

338
00:20:42,590 --> 00:20:43,480
Exactly.

339
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:44,500
She and Feng Shiye

340
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:46,120
already had a child together.

341
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:47,520
Just a disgraced woman.

342
00:20:51,460 --> 00:20:52,590
Where are you going?

343
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:53,920
Master.

344
00:20:54,280 --> 00:20:55,410
They're spouting nonsense.

345
00:20:55,410 --> 00:20:56,340
But they're not wrong.

346
00:20:56,340 --> 00:20:57,650
They are.

347
00:21:02,220 --> 00:21:03,460
What's wrong then?

348
00:21:03,950 --> 00:21:06,260
Wasn't it me who endured humiliation

349
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,410
in the enemy's camp?

350
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:09,720
Wasn't it me who got pregnant

351
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,430
with Feng Shiye's child?

352
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:16,330
Just a body.

353
00:21:16,730 --> 00:21:18,530
Why all the fuss?

354
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:21,450
What chastity and purity?

355
00:21:21,470 --> 00:21:23,550
What flawless virtue?

356
00:21:24,670 --> 00:21:26,830
On the battlefield,
I've seen all kinds of mangled limbs.

357
00:21:26,830 --> 00:21:28,310
I don't find them ugly.

358
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:30,080
I have all my limbs.

359
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:31,650
Why should I feel shame?

360
00:21:31,860 --> 00:21:34,080
That set of hollow virtues,

361
00:21:34,370 --> 00:21:35,900
you all treat as sacred law.

362
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,740
But don't try to bind me with them.

363
00:21:41,020 --> 00:21:42,950
The world may not know you, Master.

364
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:44,660
But I do.

365
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:51,020
If you were truly different from others,

366
00:21:51,020 --> 00:21:53,530
you wouldn't have thought of marrying me.

367
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:01,140
Rumors can shatter gold.

368
00:22:01,140 --> 00:22:02,440
And slander can grind bones.

369
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:03,910
I just don't want you

370
00:22:04,340 --> 00:22:05,900
to be hurt by gossip.

371
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,630
I, Mo Qingchuan,

372
00:22:08,650 --> 00:22:10,220
did it, then I did it.

373
00:22:10,350 --> 00:22:11,750
Why fear judgment?

374
00:22:11,770 --> 00:22:13,230
Why care about whispers?

375
00:22:13,430 --> 00:22:15,330
Do I need you to beg the Empress Dowager?

376
00:22:15,330 --> 00:22:16,400
Does it work?

377
00:22:17,300 --> 00:22:18,900
Do you think when your father

378
00:22:18,930 --> 00:22:20,330
begged the assassin to spare his life,

379
00:22:20,330 --> 00:22:21,440
it helped?

380
00:22:24,590 --> 00:22:25,740
You're angry?

381
00:22:26,790 --> 00:22:28,000
Good.

382
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:30,070
Don't ever let me hear

383
00:22:30,100 --> 00:22:31,830
the word "beg" from your mouth.

384
00:22:32,180 --> 00:22:33,380
Remember.

385
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:35,210
Nothing in this world

386
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:36,570
is obtained by begging.

387
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:43,240
It's not just for others' opinions,

388
00:22:43,290 --> 00:22:44,290
it's also because

389
00:22:45,500 --> 00:22:46,980
as a soldier of Xia,

390
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:48,880
I cannot stand by

391
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:51,210
and watch a helpless woman be humiliated.

392
00:22:52,230 --> 00:22:53,560
A helpless woman?

393
00:22:54,770 --> 00:22:55,400
Who?

394
00:22:56,300 --> 00:22:57,140
Me?

395
00:22:57,780 --> 00:22:59,190
In my eyes, Master,

396
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:05,240
you're still a woman.

397
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:08,460
Still someone who needs protection.

398
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:15,000
Xia Qiguang.

399
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:17,960
What are you thinking?

400
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:21,240
I mean to say...

401
00:23:22,490 --> 00:23:23,460
I mean to say...

402
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:25,290
Whatever he can help you with,

403
00:23:25,290 --> 00:23:26,560
I can do it too.

404
00:23:29,550 --> 00:23:30,270
Yes.

405
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:32,830
He is despicable and shameless.

406
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:34,770
But to deal with villains,

407
00:23:34,790 --> 00:23:36,250
one must unleash a mad dog.

408
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:39,110
My agreement with him
has nothing to do with you.

409
00:23:39,110 --> 00:23:40,350
From now on,

410
00:23:41,070 --> 00:23:43,000
you need not walk this path with me.

411
00:23:45,570 --> 00:23:46,620
I won't let him

412
00:23:46,860 --> 00:23:48,230
sway your resolve.

413
00:23:48,690 --> 00:23:49,860
Resolve?

414
00:23:50,380 --> 00:23:51,800
What resolve do I have left?

415
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:52,840
Master.

416
00:23:53,270 --> 00:23:54,600
Trust me just this once.

417
00:23:55,390 --> 00:23:56,510
What you've lost,

418
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:58,180
I'll help you reclaim.

419
00:24:02,890 --> 00:24:04,440
If the road ahead is hard,

420
00:24:04,990 --> 00:24:06,270
I'll be your vanguard.

421
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:26,330
[Qingxin Cottage]

422
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:32,270
Master went fishing alone,

423
00:24:32,290 --> 00:24:34,080
refused to let me go along.

424
00:24:34,750 --> 00:24:36,710
So dull.

425
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:41,270
Maybe I should

426
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:42,960
wander around the palace?

427
00:24:45,390 --> 00:24:46,120
Who's there?

428
00:24:54,430 --> 00:25:01,260
[Master]

429
00:25:21,320 --> 00:25:22,880
If I want sweets in the future,

430
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:24,310
can I come to you?

431
00:25:26,180 --> 00:25:27,620
That depends on my mood.

432
00:25:27,650 --> 00:25:29,000
I'm not someone

433
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:30,110
who gives kids

434
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:31,970
candied hawthorn for free.

435
00:25:32,140 --> 00:25:33,100
I'm

436
00:25:33,130 --> 00:25:35,990
the kind of person
who makes others tremble in fear.

437
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:42,680
Already bought the candied hawthorn.

438
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,880
But she won't come.

439
00:25:44,470 --> 00:25:46,030
Did I scare her off?

440
00:25:47,820 --> 00:25:48,960
At worst

441
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:51,160
I'll give it to some other kid.

442
00:25:53,030 --> 00:25:54,160
Forget it.

443
00:25:58,400 --> 00:26:00,060
About the marriage alliance,

444
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:02,500
have Your Majesty come to a decision?

445
00:26:02,560 --> 00:26:04,560
If General Mo is unwilling to marry,

446
00:26:04,660 --> 00:26:06,250
who can force her?

447
00:26:07,730 --> 00:26:09,480
Waiving thirty percent
of the tribute isn't enough?

448
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:12,060
Mo Qingchuan is no ordinary woman.

449
00:26:12,170 --> 00:26:13,830
With General Mo present,

450
00:26:13,860 --> 00:26:15,480
the Mo Army remains intact.

451
00:26:15,510 --> 00:26:17,030
Then perhaps

452
00:26:17,050 --> 00:26:19,580
these peace talks are unnecessary.

453
00:26:19,750 --> 00:26:21,270
If negotiations fail,

454
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:24,030
do Your Majesty truly believe
a mere woman like Mo Qingchuan

455
00:26:24,030 --> 00:26:25,680
can defend the border?

456
00:26:26,810 --> 00:26:29,870
If we can't supply your requested tribute,

457
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:32,490
then I have no
choice but to believe in her.

458
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:40,620
However,

459
00:26:50,100 --> 00:26:53,190
if your country could
reduce another twenty percent,

460
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:56,190
this matter

461
00:26:56,220 --> 00:27:00,580
might still be negotiable.

462
00:27:04,540 --> 00:27:07,290
Why does Your Majesty
favor chrysanthemums?

463
00:27:13,230 --> 00:27:14,490
Your Majesty.

464
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:16,530
If you grow too greedy,

465
00:27:17,130 --> 00:27:19,810
this may be the last
season your chrysanthemums

466
00:27:22,900 --> 00:27:24,510
bloom in the palace.

467
00:27:26,970 --> 00:27:28,480
What do you mean?

468
00:27:29,030 --> 00:27:30,090
Your Majesty, bad news.

469
00:27:30,090 --> 00:27:30,610
Your...

470
00:27:30,870 --> 00:27:32,600
Your golden chrysanthemum...

471
00:28:01,930 --> 00:28:03,720
Among them,

472
00:28:04,760 --> 00:28:07,330
who is truly Feng Shiye's man?

473
00:28:09,170 --> 00:28:10,310
There are only three days left

474
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:11,550
until Mo Qingchuan's
departure for marriage

475
00:28:11,550 --> 00:28:13,270
and the signing of the treaty.

476
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,030
This time,

477
00:28:17,290 --> 00:28:19,020
you must give it serious

478
00:28:20,410 --> 00:28:22,130
thought.
